"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-03-20-paris-caters-olympic-romance-220000-free-condoms\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP)- Organisers of the Paris Olympics are to distribute 220,000 condoms to athletes who want to get romantic during this year's Games in the City of Love.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995154974309431, \"rank\": 0.00034396158888588157, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP)- Organisers\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 31}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"220,000 condoms\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 87}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Games\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 149}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 161}, {\"ngram\": \"Love\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although they might be focused on sport, competitors will be free to indulge in sex if they wish - unlike during the last COVID-hit Olympics in Tokyo when they were urged to \\\"avoid unnecessary forms of physical contact\\\".\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999974160206608, \"rank\": 2.4531285462218268e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 211}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 224}, {\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 255}, {\"ngram\": \"the last COVID-hit Olympics\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"unnecessary forms\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"physical contact\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 200,000 condoms for men and 20,000 for women will be made available at the athletes' village during the Games from July 26-August 11, said Laurent Dalard, in charge of first aid and health services at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999995964117, \"rank\": 4.03533750907647e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Around 200,000 condoms\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"-August\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"Laurent Dalard\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"first aid and health services\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not know how many people are likely to use them and obviously we will adapt to the requirements if needed,\\\" he told reporters on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how many people\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"the requirements\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few thousand condoms were first distributed for free to athletes at the Seoul Olympics in 1988 to encourage safe sex and raise awareness about the HIV-AIDS epidemic sweeping the world at the time.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A few thousand condoms\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"the Seoul Olympics\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"safe sex\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"awareness\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"the HIV-AIDS epidemic\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, it has become a tradition for each event, stoking the idea of the village as a hotbed of high-performance promiscuity.\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tradition\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"each event\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"a hotbed\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"high-performance promiscuity\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The number of condoms distributed has increased dramatically over the decades, rising to 50,000 at the 1992 Barcelona Olympics, 100,000 in Beijing in 2008, and 150,000 in London in 2012.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999965543377376, \"rank\": 2.085356314666101e-06, \"text\": \"1992 Barcelona Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1201, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999993547016665, \"rank\": 6.44366