 9,000 during the Paralympics afterwards.\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2145, \"end\": 2151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9043780753420352, \"rank\": 0.09484312426754742, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic village\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"a northern suburb\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"around 14,000 people\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The site will include the usual catering area for athletes, serving food 24 hours a day, as well as a sports bar and games areas.\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The site\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"the usual catering area\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No alcohol will be served, however.\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No alcohol\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a place for parties,\\\" Laurent Michaud, director of village operations for the organising committee, told reporters on a recent tour of the village.\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"parties\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" Laurent Michaud\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"village operations\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"a recent tour\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If they want to party, they can go into Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2646, \"end\": 2651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999921230938, \"rank\": 7.876815242405e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One senior Paris organiser poured cold water on some of the fantasies around the village, telling AFP recently that he expected most of the condoms to be taken home as souvenirs or freebies.\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2666, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999921230938, \"rank\": 7.876815242405e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2753, \"end\": 2756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999997237021416, \"rank\": 2.761163190579772e-07, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cold water\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"the fantasies\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"the condoms\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2802}, {\"ngram\": \"souvenirs\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2832}, {\"ngram\": \"freebies\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES Comments are closed.\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES Comments\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2867}]}]}"